This demo directory has a number of scripts to demonstrate, excerize and
benchmark MIRIAD for a heterogeneous CARMA array.

Data:
=====
casc.vla		11.2 GHz continuum map of Cas A at 0.4" pixel	
sat1mm.modj2		225 GHz (1mm) map of Saturn, but used from optical

